						<summary>

						<p>It records the gift of money (<hi rend="italic">one achchu</hi>) for a twilight lamp to the temple of Piṇakkaṟukku nāyanār at Malaiyaḍikkuṟichchi, a southern hamlet of Śri Parāntakachchaturvēdimaṅgalam, a <hi rend="italic">brahmadēya</hi> in Āri-nāḍu by Dēvaṉ Śrīkumaran, native of Orutāḻaipaḷḷi in Malai-maṇḍalam.</p>						

